item.title: About
item.description:
Summary I am a software engineering student / web developer / open source lover from Melbourne, Australia. Loves Javascript and the web Functional Programming Go Distributed Computing Learning Projects Typescript Dependency Explorer A prototype/exploration into a novel UI for navigating dependencies in TypeScript projects.
Check it out on GitHub! Speaking 2017 “Getting started with Testing in JavaScript” at the Free Code Camp meetup, January 2017 in Melbourne.
